## #  1 more variable: week_admitted <week>
p1 <- incidence_full %>%
  group_by(week_admitted) %>%
  tally() %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_step(aes(x = week_admitted, y = n)) +
  scale_x_yearweek(
    "Week admitted",
    breaks = as.Date(as.character(2000:2023), format = "%Y"),
    date_labels = "%Y"
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous("Case admission", limits = c(0, 3500))
p1

ggsave("test_p1.svg")
## Saving 7 x 5 in image
p2 <- incidence_full %>%
  filter(status == "in-patient") %>%
  group_by(week_admitted) %>%
  tally() %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_step(aes(x = week_admitted, y = n)) +
  scale_x_yearweek(
    "Week admitted",
    breaks = as.Date(as.character(2000:2023), format = "%Y"),
    date_labels = "%Y"
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous("Case admission", limits = c(0, 3500))
p2

ggsave("test_p2.svg")
